


🛒 E-Commerce Marketplace
Complete Database Design Document
Daraz-like Multi-Vendor Platform


📋 Project
E-commerce Store
👤 Client
Rana Awais
🏢 Company
Labverse
🗄️ Database
PostgreSQL + TypeORM



Total Tables: 28  |  Modules: 10  |  Version: 1.0

📊 Database Overview

Yeh document E-Commerce platform ke complete database design ko cover karta hai. Har module ki tables, columns, data types aur relationships yahan detail mein explain ki gayi hain.

Module
Tables
Count
🔐 Auth & Users
users, roles, permissions, sessions, addresses
5
🏪 Sellers & Stores
sellers, stores
2
📦 Products
products, product_variants, product_images, categories, brands
5
🛒 Cart
carts, cart_items
2
📋 Orders
orders, order_items, shipments
3
💳 Payments & Refunds
payments, refunds
2
⭐ Reviews
reviews, ratings
2
🎯 Marketing
vouchers, campaigns, flash_sales, campaign_products
4
🔔 Notifications
notifications
1
💰 Wallet
seller_wallets, wallet_transactions
2



🔐 MODULE 1 – AUTH & USERS


1.1 users
Platform ke sab users (Customer, Seller, Admin) is table mein hain.

Column
Data Type
Constraints
Description
🔑 id
UUID
PK, DEFAULT uuid_generate_v4()
Unique identifier
name
VARCHAR(100)
NOT NULL
