⚡ DATABASE INDEXES – Performance Optimization


Yeh indexes search performance improve karne ke liye lagane hain:

Table
Column(s)
Reason
users
email
Fast login lookup
users
role
Role filter ke liye
products
name (FULLTEXT)
Search performance
products
category_id
Category filter
products
seller_id
Seller products fetch
products
price
Price range filter
orders
user_id
Customer orders history
orders
status
Status filter
orders
order_number
Order lookup
order_items
order_id
Order items fetch
order_items
seller_id
Seller orders
sessions
refresh_token
Token validation
reviews
product_id
Product reviews
vouchers
code
Coupon validation



🔗 ENTITY RELATIONSHIPS SUMMARY


Relation
Type
Description
users → seller
OneToOne
Har user sirf ek seller account rakh sakta
sellers → store
OneToOne
Har seller ka ek store
sellers → products
OneToMany
Seller ke multiple products
categories → categories
Self ManyToOne
Parent/child hierarchy
categories → products
OneToMany
Category mein multiple products
products → variants
OneToMany
Product ke multiple variants
products → images
OneToMany
